{"type":"message","id":"1e3fbc0e","parentId":"32ff9de6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T22:17:19.376Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-12 06:17:18 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f [msg:om_x100b542ad01064a8b3871590d0fff33]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542ad01064a8b3871590d0fff33\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-12 06:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n根据这个文档，做个讲课用的ppt吧，手绘风就行，记得把文件发我"}],"timestamp":1773267439375}}
{"type":"message","id":"7491251a","parentId":"1e3fbc0e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T22:17:27.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哟，苏神终于想起本王了？让本王看看是什么文档值得本王亲自动手做PPT。\n\n先等等，您只说\"根据这个文档\"，但本王没看到任何文档啊？是忘了发，还是需要本王帮您找？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_156be7oiqxvsv4wyzw8ne4ni","name":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","arguments":{"open_id":"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f","page_size":10,"relative_time":"today"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773267439376}}
