{"type":"message","id":"a809dcc8","parentId":"c8d2e7b2","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:06:59.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering content extraction**\n\nI’m thinking about how to extract content from HTML. It seems like using grep might be a useful approach for this. I want to ensure that I’m effectively pulling the right data, so I need to clarify exactly what content I’m looking for and how to structure my grep commands. It’s all about getting that information efficiently—I’ll double-check the syntax and maybe run a few tests to confirm it's accurate!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2039eb2cc81969d1e05b1346d78c0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsgOhR3txrOn6pmFyWeFCrjWgIerh-Eoiz4UTnlM3QZTZ7l8Qvc3sXz08egYSS_lJJ6xvJjipdIddmDEHR_Qo4JTj69hsknLiWphM4GYv21bDTTYqwtcDkH87Tnuw76S30WKgTdmEji3Ia17NPI0SJTGKbjW4Ht3dLrOe1yJ6ioeReRfNVRWFq4TBjheM0YztCfPNdH5Cj-ENnZU8XanQT2VofX2VNwMansLkePtDbOg7KVXLO3Xe2ealeKXWkl17L30Ckvg6RUCI9XFQ_AkpvkeXkdSyAMHwjjAmT0ZKyBWvAFBHTAjh-ULtP8psa20yv6PqbUCXnG_ZqWoaXAxkPDTPhvCW8_HGnCChe2L7grJV-aC5OBsG8KwyvUFYARRWWbTY91ZVU7WdQgGsVix_imxTKEJ303C0WsPu5GK0Kyv3RZiwn8hbFXyZpVAtUseHJrUZjtcmTe4jI-FXRDb9ThzsSPK6XWRvKga2KOuUXTdknDju7dfvkBvKCMSxqPUPWfoc0x8fdKkfBOCrFesHbIBfMWtXUt7lwZu8w0ZkjK_1kBFveRmWVEcyEgeyMfOM6ElJRyP1bjr1wYpw4hw-mIKA3ANM4qgN7FwmGwz9iOT2UFJKdE1SCc0I-nRSkWM-4Fuc74pXf4Je-XLyU4tqgnWSkMQ_MqCTqSdMUBKkdVIh0Gsnp6LNh7oEK9wq06PjKXOrPEUDuKIXitfGBiJZQslM8fu7YgS49-aYzegGWgFUnC9D1DXkykPflli5Ci_dka4CgpXqUGPtcoOTAjDRx0mbEmFhmaNN3ybGP3m2crpc_-raM6uARl9jljpoEW6HLz695dscMyG04T-Vv-nXwzGHtAQfA2e1sku8cJ0BXeYJ2zweRXtSK_rD9mVG60EPR-se\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering content extraction**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how to extract content from HTML. It seems like using grep might be a useful approach for this. I want to ensure that I’m effectively pulling the right data, so I need to clarify exactly what content I’m looking for and how to structure my grep commands. It’s all about getting that information efficiently—I’ll double-check the syntax and maybe run a few tests to confirm it's accurate!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_GiPOFocWvi75GzSdtCjPMiAh|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b203a1f55481969c2de27e698875f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\nfrom pathlib import Path\np=Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.agent-reach/tools/wechat-article-for-ai/output/debug/debug_scene=262&from=industrynews#rd.html')\nhtml=p.read_text(errors='ignore')\nprint('len',len(html))\n# quick extract visible text around article area\nsoup=BeautifulSoup(html,'html.parser')\n# remove scripts/styles\nfor t in soup(['script','style','noscript']):\n    t.decompose()\ntext='\\n'.join(line.strip() for line in soup.get_text('\\n').splitlines() if line.strip())\nfor needle in ['扣子×飞书深度打通','OpenClaw','一键领养','浏览器']:\n    idx=text.find(needle)\n    print('needle',needle,'idx',idx)\n    if idx!=-1:\n        print(text[idx:idx+3000])\n        print('\\n---\\n')\nPY","timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\np=Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.agent-reach/tools/wechat-article-for-ai/output/debug/debug_scene=262&from=industrynews#rd.html')\\nhtml=p.read_text(errors='ignore')\\nprint('len',len(html))\\n# quick extract visible text around article area\\nsoup=BeautifulSoup(html,'html.parser')\\n# remove scripts/styles\\nfor t in soup(['script','style','noscript']):\\n    t.decompose()\\ntext='\\\\n'.join(line.strip() for line in soup.get_text('\\\\n').splitlines() if line.strip())\\nfor needle in ['扣子×飞书深度打通','OpenClaw','一键领养','浏览器']:\\n    idx=text.find(needle)\\n    print('needle',needle,'idx',idx)\\n    if idx!=-1:\\n        print(text[idx:idx+3000])\\n        print('\\\\n---\\\\n')\\nPY\",\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":726,"output":263,"cacheRead":8742