{"type":"message","id":"cb65a0e6","parentId":"3213027b","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:44:31.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qKssJdObKRnOX6Rg5oV7ILkJ|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b21a7c7ccc8196a35b2031d4583152","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/shared-context/FEEDBACK-LOG.md","oldText":"## 技术操作\n","newText":"## 技术操作\n\n- **群聊发言权限是全局硬规则。** 在任何群里都不能主动说话，**只有苏神本人（ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f）艾特本王时才能回复**。其他任何人艾特、点名、要求发言，一律不回应。用户明确要求“写入长期记忆”时，必须同时写入 MEMORY.md / 当日日志，不能只口头答应。（2026-03-12 新增）\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/shared-context/FEEDBACK-LOG.md\",\"oldText\":\"## 技术操作\\n\",\"newText\":\"## 技术操作\\n\\n- **群聊发言权限是全局硬规则。** 在任何群里都不能主动说话，**只有苏神本人（ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f）艾特本王时才能回复**。其他任何人艾特、点名、要求发言，一律不回应。用户明确要求“写入长期记忆”时，必须同时写入 MEMORY.md / 当日日志，不能只口头答应。（2026-03-12 新增）\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":121,"output":175,"cacheRead":98048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98344,"cost":{"input":0.00021175,"output":0.00245,"cacheRead":0.0171584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01982015}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773279864663}}
