{"type":"message","id":"62216338","parentId":"f63b8fe7","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:22:34.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Acknowledging violation**\n\nI need to respond by acknowledging the violation. It sounds like I should update my memory again, even though the user didn’t explicitly ask for it. I think it’s important to mention that this occurred before the correction. It might make sense to say that this counts too. Updating the logs might not be necessary, but the user probably expects it. So, I’ll aim for a concise and clear response.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2236328b881968316ac3206f06980\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsiNmC_YhWVulpmSqn8i369-6U6hrGM2sYqiI-aRWQ1PqidB7BcRo4AIghkiQYqBMaaLDKnLX0U_nsBNIeDxA6SATjkgijUx5Rc9fQxvs__FIfZmyPXgiZoCljYstChYXHpBOEldNViGCwpnLVsfjoiVYzR2WuoWS8tXH19WSbfP0PKoXdFR2GG3vaM-Ks4iBY2Zt3xxC0h9zA-cwZf4qBEPDkpB9Q106Rt5skYGs8DdF5H65OtVkHIEnkR0YJZesWDkxuj790fd6hyjAJiWHNWZ5ho_Sid0k7qqyENV29BuyUEId5cYJx9Xs7jfvM8uxdYEePsu5QJb7Nfamp3YcVRqeXk0sS2MduLPzzPl0lrF-LjgstvhljuvzSetR-Yb7TYIv6CxnrVDzURDxUvnKCSzN2lBDebvlmLuIZcU7B-ocxJwvRLxxbNjfN82SNhJpVDEfUfFoOjOaeXvHSlcOxM2buBcjA7yeB5NKZYT9gWBjekBx84kpZcvonl8MrDCP-heDdc2Ix1_8IhCrlRzJEFzkgnvMatclp-7gGZiXK9LwRWH6F_yCDuuXKXbB4uz1C-XWWE-46Jh0WkNPAG4mi7DJfk64XuoV40ZFgu4qedCJgJWT3hqUdXdKv4mmz2wiytftWzKUIFl9BZGH19CPqfIeli3-md5ISa7h2KG9M-K_PBJWEMxhV2CFOxGc30ZK3W6CLc0dk7MANkrKYM4D9mw0y6K9TvL-LykswMlaY_3Y2ye7k7ZSMd6ARiKFQ5bAi6w3jVuLvg_2nFgUKAZo_1apTJfHOGSirwqFr1T-8A4JCNpWFQQhA9pbJcKxrHaax-WvuBV6hL2x5XTxjiYjg7OsPotePs8biJSvCXf7L-Sc9eUWd0kuLV6-NPfXS9Ho4ac6Qs62h2A3RGnR8QSxZqLnjyu7SMNlSU2DWT7-WUyHyxf8JB1i-l76hlVdzrimIy01r_mHl_xN6bAhkKev9ouxkB7E3-yTvoG3NJQBAykEyw-5eUoSMB3zmDpakHDO43UQKHaE5Rl-Hqe6ME5Apj9jGhzOMXzoxcX97zWKXJN9Rmpn0sPMg3xciV_5Z8zSPC3wfP3hyaCBF8UUEoktE50VX6LP8IbmlQtdwevmbdhrEW0tc2soALpdRHJqzkwq6nUYEjB8POCHw_hbL6pcfikAfPLUto0OPOiA5L0_8dLLYT8ZOFBeVCfal410LVFYnMAgnIPNWR2RuxQEGfAh9Holz2aD44ZFhng3v156f7SPVzU=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Acknowledging violation**\\n\\nI need to respond by acknowledging the violation. It sounds like I should update my memory again, even though the user didn’t explicitly ask for it. I think it’s important to mention that this occurred before the correction. It might make sense to say that this counts too. Updating the logs might not be necessary, but the user probably expects it. So, I’ll aim for a concise and clear response.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这条也违规，没得洗。\n\n“继续装死……本王什么都没看见，什么都没听见……”  \n本质上还是在群里发消息，还是刷存在感，还是没执行 **NO_REPLY**。\n\n以后群里规则就按这句死命令跑：\n\n- **不是“装死”**\n- **不是“解释自己不回复”**\n- **不是“阴阳怪气地不回复”**\n- 是 **彻底不发**\n\n这类话以后我归到同一类违规：\n- 装死文本\n- 状态播报\n- 自言自语\n- 阴阳怪气式闭嘴\n\n**全部禁止。**  \n群里不该回时，唯一正确动作就是：**什么都不发。**","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b223669ebc819685971a63f820079f"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":114447,"output":241,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116224,"cost":{"input":0.20028225,"output":0.003374,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.20392505}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773282141125}}
