{"type":"message","id":"05f913ca","parentId":"3711b451","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:42:30.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b228100d5881969dee747405dba0be\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsigRkOIwnq1vTEAOH_ICiWMbs_5ZHbT0TqrDT-z7hmD4wbH-BysCuRG-feadGzhb7eMWUrFxuJ41OSIw66SppmF1L29Yqd7qlbr5jDwm7C6qcksakHEUO03UzsMY5Jqtz3OxSaxLeK9RAJlDtyh7tZjEwDnWydZKwfv_yPnOktzh4bxfZnA4GAAzre-b-Id-v2uHXgKZy1d06c8WobCSm6kelZxRb3pSb52N5dLZ4wsVBfyvt_ZeYgnA9BXMwHt2IKYX7vOIjZL_yy1gWcuF8RXf3QAC4Ypfc_GKu9Hw3FRyn2EtdaWTFz8lz3ickuNi0lzAxQ-MAYJ05gqewIrR8lbs1dJ647Lmy3DB5F98AgOgU4LodoT4DDgPIdmemVKooi95s9LXWXzzk_vGywf3ah_TCxKLPUCQ7UsgMhAhvA7hikc1rQ_Lbk-UTMgA9yPd6QgPhs-CXiabYVWgQOofttx4DeDWcGw3hKW1Ys9mCyT2ML9AjOyu6QZlQ0Q6NiHI91IfSMFrcc1cN34FgoMs9N1jegY77N5G1fN9cq8npnEQuKkMrcp_Jje10PNV1tjdtOKbxR0VkqvDOcYVOIkErKDgVUEbRbJfpGjPYERQqJbzPOdGWBmm5kVzujWTL8NEjjMUDD-Qu_lOs-xZRG1Lna3-UdFs2I2Hq9sl0AyHGqeCEBKq2Iwg_Odbv_BHZgHpbLbSyv66Xxszd8pPF51XkP_1csg2zM4KQyj799C2fLbzxDt8D4_h0o0MwtlnrF8nfImjSh-MOAxde5iPaMuA26Zi0x8-yHGL5eMr8k3bhMBSO3hG9HD-rrS-dd_UJmuPDhclYcoIfALomC1mq9sG_82YAOSMh_ODY3dMQESy4sYjX5s=\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 能，但前提不是靠本王脑补记住，得 **写进文件**。\n\n本王现在这套“记住”的正确姿势是：\n\n- 短期上下文 → 当场记得\n- 长期规则/偏好/流程 → **写进 `MEMORY.md` / `FEEDBACK-LOG.md` / 当日日志**\n- 只有写进去，才叫真的记住\n- 不写，过会儿就可能像鱼一样失忆，虽然本王是虾，但道理一样\n\n所以你说的“第二个文档”，如果你是问：\n\n### 1）我做完 `VALIDATION-GUIDE.md` 之后，能不能长期记住？\n**能。**\n因为我会把它变成：\n- 一份正式文档\n- 再把核心规则同步进长期记忆文件\n\n### 2）只靠你现在口头说一下，我能不能永远不忘？\n**不能保证。**\n本王不装神，**文件记忆 > 脑内记忆**。\n\n所以最稳的做法是：\n> **做好第二个文档，再把结论写进长期记忆。**\n\n这样后面你再问，本王就不是“好像记得”，而是能按文件原样执行。\n\n你要是点头，本王就直接把那个  \n**`shared-context/VALIDATION-GUIDE.md`** 给你起草出来。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b228110c3081968839ca60b485c734"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":119204,"output":336,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121076