{"type":"message","id":"232e1619","parentId":"0ed8e06a","timestamp":"2026-03-12T04:05:12.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Addressing duration issues**\n\nI need to provide a concise answer regarding the duration issue in memory. I should inspect the memory and feedback, possibly mentioning the correct chain and the bug that sets the duration to 0. The user asked about finding memory, and I can explain that the duration 0 made it unplayable. The process output showed a duration of -1.0s, likely due to the script setting it to 0ms. I should consider fixing this by using .duration or ffprobe on the generated opus before providing a solution.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23b6e15308196b353c9d53c034b03\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsjtzZCnHaMjIQ99uMMGdtLLjSCFRqUho_9K2BfXzRONQcs6zfcvYaia0gYXldi0yDsD1qrObRQHc2Pce6I0vgw-eVTGRNu7ETyBv32yzJG-Kwdp_1zTwHUkpdtTq1ki99qKZK93495HVsKBwn8CFXkYmYvpB7JNxo8W5u7sV_6Kd7I2lUl_NFUMlk-hvAyu8vJO1d7XAhFMgVXTsXtR6DxvDkkRd5_YsT9plr1OEIeZu3hcXckzshJN9zwpTRLiiFqyFUM1X9Zoaw8yj7-XZu5GIOSCiwdF5bg--9KaDzn5laEeHsbImjouk0omHkyH4NGSrlvtQ3s2hRjSaEX2iQrxYtRX7IFwLiGckgacaBM45nPOKIObc9kAewZ5qdSIkEaFpOuoJxSpLZa5bcqM7HJIF3B7YkJUXGheWNBdPgQWZssaNVXhEmEV6t0SJ7zoyO7njxVVMyEmT-7RksaiKgNFh0uKenkah2TtU1tMXswSoElUwaQuR0JqK_BvA2FnNHVkwPVimc4b9mMGRvtqEyTXFRsFteHRWZZ4Qdh7Y_K1E1IaOxCqkR4Hn_oWxKEcr97vOHvvZNgpbBQuX9AMsa1B_sPcT-BmPTfxrWf7nbhxfPT83GIasnc9EhdUTrOyXlrE0y4fN6swhww-Ncu4DMsXX1f7giXUC8QT5AgcZ-lfhhv8D4uySEmNYIz0Euw3almFEcogKpcR2eHCmM47XI5IGtINPnfU3GrMX4RDv--hB0fUxL93kI0xeVMDwSpaEzkbb3VXjTMf99emaJxIc-I3nIohxpNoeZFl5oAFaYOUW85rK_uFNaAig0hZEggcofcz0LJ4EpMPGEzey5UnUTrCEed9cd1c3PXb_GXl2JFqgP9ldTUo2sOkYjbXNp9urwkTBmI3zzCNbF4w0JqIvN5RM_JmsecJU9ToY7hlzB1LoHOjwIaglc3JMrRPAjC-sUewK9hVlV8Y6H5hcEUnG1y2ew3O2OWelDjJIIQoQjYKrzmpsQP3xZDgOiAStPDomxL6tsIEKOZO5pfnvatqZXMI2HMTEp3YDXnIgQkwLYNvMlQZ8AnbaUCc_IWdFt7uo4ByvIxuB-50O-DTdKuiYWb4KiYj2ZCOoivfJre4bPk-7lf_oBrWy09cclxa2-q_mo5Xgk1fCsLx