ary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Fixing voice duration issues**\\n\\nI need to address the voice fix, and I might want to use a script while making sure the duration is correct. It seems I could edit the script to use ffprobe on the Opus output if its duration is negative. I could also manually generate Opus with reference audio, check the duration with ffprobe, and then write the duration to send. But wait, it looks like I don’t need to read up on any additional developer skills for now.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"行，这次本王不赌运气，先把时长算准，再发。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23c3e63c481969c783b82f5aa9110"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ib87roEskYlSUzbrbuQ4JAIC|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23c3e6f6c81968d2810ec85bd3aa0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\nOPUS=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-voice-XXXXXX.opus)\nDUR=${OPUS%.opus}.duration\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\n  --output \"$OPUS\" \\\n  --format opus \\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\n  --ref-audio '/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629' \\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts.log; exit 1; }\npython3 - <<'PY' \"$OPUS\" \"$DUR\"\nimport subprocess,sys,pathlib,re\nopus=sys.argv[1]; durf=sys.argv[2]\ndur=None\nfor cmd in [\n    ['ffprobe','-v','error','-show_entries','format=duration','-of','default=nk=1:nw=1',opus],\n    ['ffprobe','-v','error','-show_entries','stream=duration','-of','default=nk=1:nw=1',opus],\n    ['afinfo',opus],\n]:\n    try:\n        out=subprocess.check_output(cmd, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT, text=True).strip()\n    except Exception:\n        continue\n    if cmd[0]=='afinfo':\n        m=re.search(r'estimated duration: ([0-9.]+)', out)\n        if m:\n            dur=float(m.group(1)); break\n    else:\n        for line in out.splitlines():\n            line=line.strip()\n            try:\n                val=float(line)\n                if val>0:\n                    dur=val; raise SystemExit\n            except:\n                pass\nif dur is None:\n    dur=8.0\npathlib.Path(durf).write_text(str(dur))\nprint(dur)\nPY\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \"$OPUS\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\n","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":180},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\nOPUS=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-voice-XXXXXX.opus)\\nDUR=${OPUS%.opus}.duration\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\\\\n  --output \\\"$OPUS\\\" \\\\\\n  --format opus \\\\\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\\\\n  --ref-audio '/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629' \\\\\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts.log; exit 1; }\\npython3 - <<'PY' \\\"$OPUS\\\" \\\"$DUR\\\"\\nimport subprocess,sys,pathlib,re\\nopus=sys.argv[1]; durf=sys.argv[2]\\ndur=None\\nfor cmd in [\\n    ['ffprobe','-v','error','-show_entries','format=duration','-of','default=nk=1:nw=1',opus],\\n    ['ffprobe','-v','error','-show_entries','stream=duration','-of','default=nk=1:nw=1',opus],\\n    ['afinfo',opus],\\n]:\\n    try:\\n        out=subprocess.check_output(cmd, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT, text=True).strip()\\n    except Exception:\\n        continue\\n    if cmd[0]=='afinfo':\\n        m=re.search(r'estimated duration: ([0-9.]+)', out)\\n        if m:\\n            dur=float(m.group(1)); break\\n    else:\\n        for line in out.splitlines():\\n            line=line.strip()\\n            try:\\n                val=float(line)\\n                if val>0:\\n                    dur=val; raise SystemExit\\n            except:\\n                pass\\nif dur is None:\\n    dur=8.0\\npathlib.Path(durf).write_text(str(dur))\\nprint(dur)\\nPY\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \\\"$OPUS\\\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\\n\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":180}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":137176,"output":689,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139401,"cost":{"input":0.240058,"output":0.009646,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.2499728}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773288498315}}
