{"type":"message","id":"d68d5bff","parentId":"82689194","timestamp":"2026-03-12T04:10:49.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering audio conversion options**\n\nI'm thinking I could use afconvert to turn WAV or M4A files into Ogg Opus format. I know the input from noiz can be in WAV, MP3, or M4A, so that's a good start. I think I need to generate a WAV file using ref-audio first and then use afconvert to convert it to Ogg Opus. Wait, I should also remember to create a duration file with afinfo. Let's go ahead and test that!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23cbd42a881969d0478891c6df351\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsjzBbDN3Da3DV82sxuX5P38pQTFnWAZDmi88keM4-IVED4eFowtk18t93W5-Vma2AKQJXT_0NAZ_xC2_UKSyOkze_MxMsrskn-9xoiHaalnb9vvLQ6PIIxi9sEI-yVw5QvuoJMN63odv3IhjtUGiCUZAkDroqtvWxUrFG2MU1j-tM1UfukC7kSJYfAVfMHn5GPMBBbC5k1RNqa15VF4QirVOthTIFOy84beFnRamOfdAMJoRvkGe8Y-7KrsQkwlRuEerEkBWUl5cAMVNkVZyeOdRuGikhLBXxdDU7fT-0Vjapspk_t4UsXlR3ZJazkXal27KAEPLnqranmNN9vIGHUPnXAEHcU4n4xKzWb8HRHjxnKTV3TKKADAuR597Kxw3XS6VqhvuhMl3qmaEui1Zd1gjI0EhnGfILz0qKfisDLFETuRccOfZlfo_aViOtlWtY3quz7HVSot4QBPOH_54FRoi1kbcRczGyCPtfAmEs6K3etLJL4v1kSRKuy_6_PvTDXJpuvGcqdBQhVs6mdcT9xgKzAhdxDUpT0R7AaSFawfqf2szuzP5j0RO4MvZ2j3e3g_eSjwrXU9_bnCCVgpDTtjNFxHajhVLHUFNCklUParepaAxsAnf6nwUnKLKTBzqT4v24jXpBWZYBEtNNqR5HEqJIaQl0F9ca8nJyO4oKwRipd9eIQk2g74JV_KCe3-OMr8hzBVy_0SipnFtl4kgYtGEI72rsy1UV7_y2ETCETqS-HBJl1n2h9g0jAdoQai3wzzA-khCPFQIhciubrR1yALkZLAUUp3tlUTL0azOUzduT1B4X_tnzvndu-_S23GDynqCaZXTh9a426qpALlxTdcKO4HazuQUSm40yHomsrSylLlHTr3dq6ydbshOmUXffYYMFi5wLp7YfXRzu3IT1e7vkkBC8iLhBIA1zL7tUVhmq-q4211dHINfDzRSmPmP650mzaJHjhPmGgphw9EbisCYwHqoNGz4N2lEUteDt-J9pphRD4FLnoISRXbedduolWBh_BzpPxxmORVoq-IkBuBWpaWJvgXxxXQQ6TzxJegD809dfC0e5M_UYtu_Jk3fHvmOmVYEumU2lAYT_dV-YxOkQkFi7Koh-VrPCTgm_UY-BY3ZrTxFWWA29AmVR4MbVZMYykLKV9socU4z4aKdU-Qg8A==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering audio conversion options**\\n\\nI'm thinking I could use afconvert to turn WAV or M4A files into Ogg Opus format. I know the input from noiz can be in WAV, MP3, or M4A, so that's a good start. I think I need to generate a WAV file using ref-audio first and then use afconvert to convert it to Ogg Opus. Wait, I should also remember to create a duration file with afinfo. Let's go ahead and test that!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"有救，机器上虽然没 ffmpeg，但有 `afconvert`，而且它支持把音频转成 **Ogg/Opus**。  \n也就是说正确链路应该改成：\n\n1. Noiz 先生成 **wav / m4a**\n2. 本地再转成 **真正的 `.opus`**\n3. 算准 duration\n4. 再发飞书语音条\n\n这次才是正道。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23cc1bb3c8196b146144cc856a850"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xQEcMSeew6A1TMvq2NKjrTL4|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23cc1e6488196a6b4368a00f6d2ed","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\nWAV=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-ref-XXXXXX.wav)\nOPUS=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-ref-XXXXXX.opus)\nDUR=${OPUS%.opus}.duration\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\n  --output \"$WAV\" \\\n  --format wav \\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\n  --ref-audio '/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629' \\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts2.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts2.log; exit 1; }\nfile \"$WAV\"\nafconvert -f Oggf -d opus \"$WAV\" \"$OPUS\"\npython3 - <<'PY' \"$WAV\" \"$DUR\"\nimport subprocess,sys,re,pathlib\nwav=sys.argv[1]; durf=sys.argv[2]\nout=subprocess.check_output(['afinfo', wav], text=True, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT)\nm=re.search(r'estimated duration: ([0-9.]+)', out)\nd=float(m.group(1)) if m else 8.0\npathlib.Path(durf).write_text(str(d))\nprint(d)\nPY\nfile \"$OPUS\"\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \"$OPUS\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\n","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":240},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\nWAV=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-ref-XXXXXX.wav)\\nOPUS=$(mktemp /tmp/xiawang-ref-XXXXXX.opus)\\nDUR=${OPUS%.opus}.duration\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\\\\n  --output \\\"$WAV\\\" \\\\\\n  --format wav \\\\\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\\\\n  --ref-audio '/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629' \\\\\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts2.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts2.log; exit 1; }\\nfile \\\"$WAV\\\"\\nafconvert -f Oggf -d opus \\\"$WAV\\\" \\\"$OPUS\\\"\\npython3 - <<'PY' \\\"$WAV\\\" \\\"$DUR\\\"\\nimport subprocess,sys,re,pathlib\\nwav=sys.argv[1]; durf=sys.argv[2]\\nout=subprocess.check_output(['afinfo', wav], text=True, stderr=subprocess.STDOUT)\\nm=re.search(r'estimated duration: ([0-9.]+)', out)\\nd=float(m.group(1)) if m else 8.0\\npathlib.Path(durf).write_text(str(d))\\nprint(d)\\nPY\\nfile \\\"$OPUS\\\"\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \\\"$OPUS\\\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\\n\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":240}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1724,"output":636,"cacheRead":141056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143416,"cost":{"input":0.003017,"output":0.008904,"cacheRead":0.0246848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0366058}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773288633498}}
