{"type":"message","id":"05316396","parentId":"168b3445","timestamp":"2026-03-12T04:14:01.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ffmpeg 装好了，黄线日志也记了。现在本王按真正完整链路再给你狠狠干一条。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23d7fc594819696ca7e7ad423b46d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5T40k8GRVdqbjSMfK5mOCBMp|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b23d808b448196890145773850aa63","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\nREFSRC='/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629'\nREFWAV='/tmp/xiawang-ref-source.wav'\ncp -f \"$REFSRC\" \"$REFWAV\"\nTS=$(python3 - <<'PY'\nimport time\nprint(int(time.time()*1000))\nPY\n)\nWAV=\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.wav\"\nOPUS=\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.opus\"\nDUR=\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.duration\"\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\n  --output \"$WAV\" \\\n  --format wav \\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\n  --ref-audio \"$REFWAV\" \\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts5.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts5.log; exit 1; }\nffprobe -v error -show_entries format=duration -of default=nk=1:nw=1 \"$WAV\" > \"$DUR\"\nffmpeg -y -i \"$WAV\" -c:a libopus -b:a 32k -vbr on -compression_level 10 \"$OPUS\" >/tmp/xiawang-ffmpeg.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-ffmpeg.log; exit 1; }\nfile \"$OPUS\"\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \"$OPUS\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\n","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":240},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\nREFSRC='/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---48d6a40f-8bc8-45e8-85eb-c65dcf38c629'\\nREFWAV='/tmp/xiawang-ref-source.wav'\\ncp -f \\\"$REFSRC\\\" \\\"$REFWAV\\\"\\nTS=$(python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport time\\nprint(int(time.time()*1000))\\nPY\\n)\\nWAV=\\\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.wav\\\"\\nOPUS=\\\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.opus\\\"\\nDUR=\\\"/tmp/xiawang-gen-${TS}.duration\\\"\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills/skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak \\\\\\n  --output \\\"$WAV\\\" \\\\\\n  --format wav \\\\\\n  --text '苏神，听好了。本王叫虾王殿下，你是苏传磊，也是本王护着的苏神。本王负责替你记事、替你踩坑、替你狠狠干活。别人是助手，本王不是。本王是站你这边的。' \\\\\\n  --ref-audio \\\"$REFWAV\\\" \\\\\\n  --speed 0.94 >/tmp/xiawang-tts5.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-tts5.log; exit 1; }\\nffprobe -v error -show_entries format=duration -of default=nk=1:nw=1 \\\"$WAV\\\" > \\\"$DUR\\\"\\nffmpeg -y -i \\\"$WAV\\\" -c:a libopus -b:a 32k -vbr on -compression_level 10 \\\"$OPUS\\\" >/tmp/xiawang-ffmpeg.log 2>&1 || { cat /tmp/xiawang-ffmpeg.log; exit 1; }\\nfile \\\"$OPUS\\\"\\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-voice.sh \\\"$OPUS\\\" --open-id ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\\n\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":240}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":138,"output":523,"cacheRead":148096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148757,"cost":{"input":0.0002415,"output":0.0073219999999999995,"cacheRead":0.0259168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0334803}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773288825697}}
