dheres to security protocols. I want to help while keeping the user’s best interests in mind! Let’s clarify this and proceed carefully.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 能装，但**不能闭眼装**。\n\n按你给本王定的安全规矩，安装新 Skill 必须走这套：\n\n1. **先看你说的是哪几个技能**\n2. **逐个安全审计**\n   - 列文件\n   - 读内容\n   - 查有没有外发、偷环境变量、`curl|sh`、base64 混淆、改核心文件之类的脏东西\n3. **审计过关再安装**\n4. 如果涉及环境变更/安装依赖，按黄线记录进当天 memory\n\n所以答案是：\n\n- **技术上能装**\n- **流程上要先审计**\n- **你把技能名 / 链接 / 仓库地址发我，本王就开干**\n\n你直接丢给我：\n- ClawHub 链接\n- GitHub 链接\n- 或者技能名字列表\n\n本王给你一条一条验。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2552bcaac819691ad3e1adde8bbff"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":166771,"output":244,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168551,"cost":{"input":0.29184925,"output":0.0034159999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.29553405}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773294872933}}
