It's also important to audit the skills, especially with the mandatory audits for installing new skills. I wonder if I should focus on a specific skill from Clawhub to ensure I'm following the right process. Let's make sure everything is in order before proceeding!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9jwzg86YAPn8DUAAMohriAXP|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b261ee96208196b243ee64e682f657","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":168087,"output":96,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":169719,"cost":{"input":0.29415225,"output":0.001344,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.29576505000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773298147070}}
{"type":"message","id":"0289375c","parentId":"36e9355e","timestamp":"2026-03-12T06:49:18.961Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9jwzg86YAPn8DUAAMohriAXP|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b261ee96208196b243ee64e682f657","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773298158953}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ddd3fab","parentId":"0289375c","timestamp":"2026-03-12T06:49:33.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating installation requirements**\n\nI need to conduct an audit before installing. Maybe I'll consider a skill-vetter, but I'm not sure about using external options. Our AGENTS suggest performing a manual audit using clawhub inspect with the --files option to read the files. So, it looks like I should start searching for the appropriate skill to help with this process! Let’s keep it simple and thorough to ensure everything is correct before proceeding.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b261f885708196a55139ba1d4a9e43\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsmH9UUXHapcRZgCZMj6pr4vsGp_L_8RSeioBzlvsda2--QgQmmPgBDuvhnGR4kslQ_NsqxSD1Li09lzx6Sy_lKlcNJ5BQNHo1AvTcCzs-jAVPf6_Tks2z1Yd6emyXICtKgFB4ugMy2k-slphDDzyJoWuSwJGgODVvpVVXnTKE1pZZDSlMWYkPSSuLLJoUh01PSyYJEcFrbNeNp7K3iQvvIgHgMWwvVpnupGLeqyZOIg_I3CnY-7qPK3RM8yaCABYtGea1_DzViMCo5isnxGGtlAWVo40VSH4_AkIAND7W47Wi_Xrjxc92TriBCBWsaKpvdtH86ryeRJHd7QxHDNXcfpD_B2QCb56pP3ajhM4B1YTbzms26bGkOHCNDY4_3ZcpWdcI1O1ZTNB38Snk2OigEbu0tJRERi3hXX9jnmHmR2mVlKPiyEwSlGV9xDaZt04bvcDc-F5GHv4_xumGcKAL1AVMX4_z6rlPEo4OnWzBfPunVndkVQrn4zS03xPVSSWekfDVA3BJXoBGG2IUAG9JUIjlPGrKJ_uGgInDfHVf0s84EmXWmR1bIj12GDjJMby7YwLmSmJAFB3sfWoc7xqxvUVssWzIPzYlo9Bd3BIjAs0rGMfam00_xQFhrGGdGlx1VOERaJRTHFTj4OuN8GIvmm7CcHWXYJF4cLZXan43mvaOZZmEyep5yyWkITRw4hAEPK9n_5go1NKyJfNsrJOnRA7C_ZHvCJ4I50iD7hOvtfqsqqxuJaApcxPyRwURKDiT27zZqXUP3JyNK-3GfhQ6wIXk8RXSuw63SeT4yIgYg4tgsTwIqWta908ADMp31WJQgHKcZ2inRYK0N_CqQOXidp4u26jC6W1Lf4rLlbZd4oW34xTxQKlDdi6cd9hIz3V8Eiq5Hgn10w7q8-CIi_AWXdaXxWplnfJMKHQW9jw_-Fn1EPRncFVw1ytellwtrpkHO1K2Q8gdm7SyIRnAl9tK6D8QOXfw6Lw6Jbx4mtSYEwedx47MfQt1PEImmyP6oG7H05l1UxOoes5SeifkVQaRpn9Mg38fqWlJ20ETgWrqwpSBVQ=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating installation requirements**\\n\\nI need to conduct an audit before installing. Maybe I'