BQbonvMT3jaRlszl-UJH9nlCCcfYxg3Dxw_x83n1zO8SPzqZjjxBAecFis5CPCEiFu\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Generating music file**\\n\\nI need to generate a song since the user asked for it. We have the skills installed, but the tool isn't directly available. I might need to use execution commands to run it. Should I use a sensitive key from before? I can source the environment bridging. After generating the song, I’ll send the resulting MP3 through a script. I need to create some lyrics for the song as well.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"好，来一首 **热血向《龙虾王朝》**。  \n本王先给你狠狠干一版带歌词的，能出声先出声，别空谈。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b27c461a0c8196ad1cc630748af87e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_j5HnOXyvt4MjYEOlsDXYuJPs|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b27c4629908196b71ce0e0153a697c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\nsource ~/.zshrc >/dev/null 2>&1 || true\nexport MINIMAX_MUSIC_API_KEY=\"${MINIMAX_MUSIC_API_KEY:-${MINIMAX_API_KEY:-}}\"\nOUTDIR=/tmp/lobster-dynasty\nmkdir -p \"$OUTDIR\"\ncat > \"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\" <<'EOF'\n[Intro]\n黑潮翻涌 战鼓震天\n赤甲燃起 火照长滩\n\n[Verse]\n我们从深海裂隙之间醒来\n钳光划破了沉默与阴霾\n旧世界的规则全都改写\n龙虾王朝 此刻登上王台\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\n别低头 别后退 别怀疑这身硬壳\n每一道伤 都会变成新的轮廓\n\n[Chorus]\n龙虾王朝 向前冲 让海面都沸腾\n这一身热血 比烈火还要更滚烫\n龙虾王朝 不服输 把命运握手中\n今日起浪潮随我号令 万军共鸣\n\n[Verse]\n不是谁赐予我们所谓荣光\n是一路硬闯 把名字刻在风浪\n当深海尽头亮起赤红旗帜\n所有沉默终将为我们鼓掌\n\n[Bridge]\n听啊 雷鸣正为我们开道\n看啊 星火在壳上燃烧\n若这时代需要一个王朝\n那就让龙虾 把传说写到最高\n\n[Chorus]\n龙虾王朝 向前冲 让海面都沸腾\n这一身热血 比烈火还要更滚烫\n龙虾王朝 不服输 把命运握手中\n今日起浪潮随我号令 万军共鸣\n\n[Outro]\n赤甲不灭 热血长明\n龙虾王朝 万浪归心\nEOF\nPROMPT='Genre: 热血摇滚 + 史诗流行 | Era: modern cinematic rock | Mood: 热血, 燃, 王者归来 | Tempo: 138 BPM | Instruments: powerful drums, electric guitar, orchestral brass, choir, bass | Vocals: powerful male lead vocal, anthemic chorus | Use case: 直播开场战歌，王朝崛起 | Avoid: no soft ballad, no cute style, no lo-fi'\ncd /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mm-music-maker\npython3 scripts/generate_music.py --lyrics \"$(cat \"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\")\" --prompt \"$PROMPT\" --output \"$OUTDIR/lobster_dynasty.mp3\"","yieldMs":1000,"background":true,"timeout":900},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\nsource ~/.zshrc >/dev/null 2>&1 || true\\nexport MINIMAX_MUSIC_API_KEY=\\\"${MINIMAX_MUSIC_API_KEY:-${MINIMAX_API_KEY:-}}\\\"\\nOUTDIR=/tmp/lobster-dynasty\\nmkdir -p \\\"$OUTDIR\\\"\\ncat > \\\"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\\\" <<'EOF'\\n[Intro]\\n黑潮翻涌 战鼓震天\\n赤甲燃起 火照长滩\\n\\n[Verse]\\n我们从深海裂隙之间醒来\\n钳光划破了沉默与阴霾\\n旧世界的规则全都改写\\n龙虾王朝 此刻登上王台\\n\\n[Pre-Chorus]\\n别低头 别后退 别怀疑这身硬壳\\n每一道伤 都会变成新的轮廓\\n\\n[Chorus]\\n龙虾王朝 向前冲 让海面都沸腾\\n这一身热血 比烈火还要更滚烫\\n龙虾王朝 不服输 把命运握手中\\n今日起浪潮随我号令 万军共鸣\\n\\n[Verse]\\n不是谁赐予我们所谓荣光\\n是一路硬闯 把名字刻在风浪\\n当深海尽头亮起赤红旗帜\\n所有沉默终将为我们鼓掌\\n\\n[Bridge]\\n听啊 雷鸣正为我们开道\\n看啊 星火在壳上燃烧\\n若这时代需要一个王朝\\n那就让龙虾 把传说写到最高\\n\\n[Chorus]\\n龙虾王朝 向前冲 让海面都沸腾\\n这一身热血 比烈火还要更滚烫\\n龙虾王朝 不服输 把命运握手中\\n今日起浪潮随我号令 万军共鸣\\n\\n[Outro]\\n赤甲不灭 热血长明\\n龙虾王朝 万浪归心\\nEOF\\nPROMPT='Genre: 热血摇滚 + 史诗流行 | Era: modern cinematic rock | Mood: 热血, 燃, 王者归来 | Tempo: 138 BPM | Instruments: powerful drums, electric guitar, orchestral brass, choir, bass | Vocals: powerful male lead vocal, anthemic chorus | Use case: 直播开场战歌，王朝崛起 | Avoid: no soft ballad, no cute style, no lo-fi'\\ncd /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mm-music-maker\\npython3 scripts/generate_music.py --lyrics \\\"$(cat \\\"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\\\")\\\" --prompt \\\"$PROMPT\\\" --output \\\"$OUTDIR/lobster_dynasty.mp3\\\"\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true,\"timeout\":900}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":372,"output":776,"cacheRead":203904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":205052,"cost":{"input":0.000651,"output":0.010864,"cacheRead":0.0356832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.047198199999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773304889192}}
