rus]\n龙虾王朝 向前冲\n赤甲燃烧 万浪共鸣\n龙虾王朝 不低头\n今天就把传奇写成\n\n[Outro]\n龙虾王朝 万浪归心\nEOF\nPROMPT='Genre: 热血摇滚 + 史诗流行 | Mood: 热血, 燃, 王者归来 | Tempo: 136 BPM | Instruments: powerful drums, electric guitar, brass, bass | Vocals: powerful male lead vocal | Use case: 战歌开场 | Avoid: no soft ballad, no cute style'\ncd /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mm-music-expert\npython3 scripts/generate_music.py --lyrics \"$(cat \"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\")\" --prompt \"$PROMPT\" --output \"$OUTDIR/lobster_dynasty_test.mp3\" --download","yieldMs":1000,"background":true,"timeout":900},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -euo pipefail\\nunset http_proxy https_proxy HTTP_PROXY HTTPS_PROXY all_proxy ALL_PROXY\\nexport MINIMAX_MUSIC_API_KEY='sk-api-Nm5Dhd8YJ-Q_hOxgekm6KDKpRgd2Pjmat8BylW4zvg1GMJDNZO48f4HmryFCLaVIO2Izjw9I-sIm4nM6MEntX79yFKL4isSxydrvLhYW6dDM8x_LJNsU19A'\\nOUTDIR=/tmp/lobster-dynasty-newkey\\nmkdir -p \\\"$OUTDIR\\\"\\ncat > \\\"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\\\" <<'EOF'\\n[Intro]\\n龙虾王朝 正在苏醒\\n\\n[Verse]\\n深海翻涌 王旗高擎\\n热血轰鸣 震碎旧命运\\n\\n[Chorus]\\n龙虾王朝 向前冲\\n赤甲燃烧 万浪共鸣\\n龙虾王朝 不低头\\n今天就把传奇写成\\n\\n[Outro]\\n龙虾王朝 万浪归心\\nEOF\\nPROMPT='Genre: 热血摇滚 + 史诗流行 | Mood: 热血, 燃, 王者归来 | Tempo: 136 BPM | Instruments: powerful drums, electric guitar, brass, bass | Vocals: powerful male lead vocal | Use case: 战歌开场 | Avoid: no soft ballad, no cute style'\\ncd /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/mm-music-expert\\npython3 scripts/generate_music.py --lyrics \\\"$(cat \\\"$OUTDIR/lyrics.txt\\\")\\\" --prompt \\\"$PROMPT\\\" --output \\\"$OUTDIR/lobster_dynasty_test.mp3\\\" --download\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true,\"timeout\":900}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":726,"output":477,"cacheRead":205952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":207155,"cost":{"input":0.0012705,"output":0.006678,"cacheRead":0.0360416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.043990100000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773305285518}}
