{"type":"message","id":"28c4bc19","parentId":"0c3818eb","timestamp":"2026-03-12T08:58:25.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 行，歌词给你：\n\n**《龙虾王朝》**\n\n[Intro]  \n龙虾王朝 正在苏醒\n\n[Verse]  \n深海翻涌 王旗高擎  \n热血轰鸣 震碎旧命运\n\n[Chorus]  \n龙虾王朝 向前冲  \n赤甲燃烧 万浪共鸣  \n龙虾王朝 不低头  \n今天就把传奇写成\n\n[Outro]  \n龙虾王朝 万浪归心\n\n如果你要，我还能顺手给你补两版：\n- **更燃一点的完整版歌词**\n- **更适合直播开场口号版**","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b28025ff688196b90566a7e58b3915"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":919,"output":153,"cacheRead":203136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":204208,"cost":{"input":0.0016082499999999999,"output":0.002142,"cacheRead":0.0355488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.039299049999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773305888941}}
