{"type":"message","id":"a8b332e4","parentId":"93dbd04b","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:47:29.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 搞定了，已经直接写进飞书文档了。\n\n标题是：\n\n**《从会聊到会干：为什么 OpenClaw 是个人智能体时代的重要入口｜90分钟直播长稿》**\n\n文档链接：  \nhttps://www.feishu.cn/docx/IZK0dc3TJonNX3xwSvwc0cRQntg\n\n这版已经是**能讲 1 个半小时的长稿版**，你可以直接拿去讲。  \n如果你愿意，本王下一步可以继续给你补两刀：\n\n1. **压成更适合现场讲的口语化提词版**\n2. **直接拆成 PPT 分页提纲版**\n\n你一句话，本王继续。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2b5dc124881969f10838d432cfb88"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":168,"output":168,"cacheRead":226944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":227280,"cost":{"input":0.000294,"output":0.002352,"cacheRead":0.0397152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0423612}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773319631305}}
