{"type":"message","id":"e4cd674c","parentId":"3fa97fdb","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:57:26.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning presentation generation**\n\nI'm thinking about creating a concise 12-slide outline first. Instead of just generating images for a PPT, I might use a markdown outline to keep things organized. Oh, should I utilize the existing baoyu-slide-deck? We’ve used custom prompts with image generation before, which could influence the style. Maybe I could write the outline and prompts with Python? Ultimately, the aim is to create a fresh outline and formal style prompts, generate images, and then merge them all together.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2b81cb3cc819690da8139a91ea8b8\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsrgr5dcfSYZOfKjl341M9t5e2WqaI_QQg_IuEMWNxXRICDaLjRFtVAXEmyj_I6IEP8ccFLHFSN66juMWFmLpgJil9BnOJkjpANa-0ikgs9fKM1ezFdPWCH46BuRAjegEGlS3XhdAIal21VgL2Lgg4fcl1qrsvAclJfi9X03aORNf5ljjHdwp7BfKbedqzZU_tQBS5ta34cjXt6F2-03in1NHYGOezfmoP0mdRYDZpRB4FHraiJ-33l7vdPclfhMc5QZ9BM312cuRp23cGc6980ABvh6Vgh4X2YZno0D4DQhFrOIdTRqFhB79TrOJWP9Nb2lxQA7BfIcDAMf9KUpdlbElEc7Pfo0egE8HBRHIjfFd-Cqs86GaIrJqzFetvgK0O_w80l51VkjfN9EbeNdAXrapyhCDYYjXZErbWsUicX7zTuBKdBjBuNVhCM59EECKAThyGviLXGIABxi7i5m7yJwki_8_ttlnQoAXSvInnMFWkIyIlTAE8HUeQE4QgFVSh6_hxtFMw9vZ4TpfIF0ItwsuxSgR2mL4k_uLS5yZMwsyliwkeRprKX99nPL76Gq2G-mA_wqlgCjbTlqvxqrUBx7udejCLGgckyROEf0s1QMvC9oJLpPdbunxoYbJo9Mf9iBsGACQL4gIUxNarZOH6zPQfeovsbX_m8rIbke_3uueyu8h8zd1fIjBL5JxRBUpyKC3ZS-Nzv7UYIke2vW4Za9ZS5pfVVvuSwSydSu7NdypV9cGVnI5NXbxJY4nl_xAswBD5rpQPOK8g4_4NADWIKisLGRtlYbHaRa8FC4gVzsHLoT0HHjoGTXgyaxNDYlNW4igYotKfrz93AmQk-TMg6RzpkrEMggBE4cUcrW_4StmgeGiXWc8HNs2iZlgNQjeuj6ZyGWhf8dnRFkP-DRxNqJ2ioo1aVMCZCyHheDcS2_pX9oUBIUh48nUf-ZYJNG6NA944bs4GymvdJ9_luN-hCv2Q1-PnUVyg_r5X2Y-HRBtAnFndiGSAs6uugmkqhRYvt8CQ0-08rPLhSSIHfoa44yqnqCDY5WUIacSR339A-_ufwkf9Oxq7MRdqXRjF8qDPb_gCCNzJ5Sr9xdD3t3N5TA2fL2WtNA_kaAElmjT2y0JpBrJWKrLGQFUyuQWTVxuSRo1ZoTzCQ