nder if I should just insert the first image with the media function instead. I’ll need to decide soon.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"还没完，本王这里卡在“**按章节精确插图**”这一步，不是图没有，是**飞书原生文档工具对“插到指定标题下面”支持不够顺手**。  \n我现在改走网页编辑，把图按章节位置塞进去，这样能对齐。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c112db908196ae5146cecb0e1077"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zY0F2Mf3IIKdEvfFMtKAJO8i|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c11302488196960deb40caa558f0","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/IZK0dc3TJonNX3xwSvwc0cRQntg","target":"host"},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"open\",\"url\":\"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/IZK0dc3TJonNX3xwSvwc0cRQntg\",\"target\":\"host\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":229877,"output":436,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":231849,"cost":{"input":0.40228474999999997,"output":0.006104,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.40865755}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773322491323}}
