{"type":"message","id":"d111cae7","parentId":"0080597a","timestamp":"2026-03-12T13:36:26.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Investigating login issues**\n\nI’m trying to figure out why logging in is impossible. Maybe the user is already logged in, but only with a specific Chrome profile. I wonder if I could use that Chrome profile instead of Openclaw or extensions? But it seems like the profile isn't currently attached. Would using a Chrome profile that’s already logged in help? I need to look into the browser to check on existing tabs and see if an extension is required.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c14ebef0819694b519c5eaeb483a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpssFZ36IvHOYxvD_IUBv0lUtFekbi_woqA4P1x3isLYFyiN1dewDx8cEQI7neTifrniIy2Jehn5tUuowxi6eXAXcznHW1dLLbAdYTurOZKMhP12V0gId0wBqK7SSCd9nIwE4FByLS52BXscW-eCkqIeXbLtUe4n5Y9IuNb2mqOWrm2Gxxy5ncbjAurito1rklG7RGmKHWL2ae3xYwYrrRGTfBbtGF5RpNeIOssIdxqMDgKyGacaTl_4sDuEWvH1ifx4GoC8tKt4sYOzK2181pIvPNtZcbACEnG-_9MZrG_sXz7cW7m4j-Fqaw1ipBIGBRnBUYCe9ZUDf47Z1EtXsx8PD4KKCS8OZTVNyKXsu7ZpUHcQy5xPnoBONk6ZfHwhawwB4SWlSXw2H7few6Fo8m4x_-kUyqXip5PGKrhnKIfEOekyC6fEz1CwfH9rDkWyxJA1wbbe1vXdqkmpl2CZ3nifCxsPo-kdCSK4dZdIYhlo6SW3AC3rO8I4SY9qqMYJ8wnB7GqgFuN5eaP5Ige2S_wUjMO7CCBvwlF2I3NI6FPhxOZN1RDmnWeni1Pb2-jEupBn6D_9tt_IcARYHtEM0wIUEIFBiGg8A5xX7KQCwOBvalF1hni5xoTBQ02pwMS-P76nh33pmF33asfVESm7SoPVZtQTp9uuBjToiAD0j6z5AouQiRrCENaUoionwnmAnNMUJScplKqfQNJG3nqfFM4r5IaZHi-Uz4b0DJGLxhEUlHTOrH2Z_dnPiIWSR5qc_NWbm-io-Ye8J2MOvW7XOREyfJSt0mwZ1kdcx2292QXWbaF27jyO7r7lvNqV3P98ROAmpoOjeH9NlNK8S6H1ugplPw7rVf_axtyoYyiWEATa2By9B47L4XJ3QqIj1M9jUZcuc7tajoaA_PSxyZ4xFNvisvRfnFd-2EEh1GptfJX60M2zRFi2Ikia_g-ERdtqdfdwGDTbcFuSIaPvhNRU5CvRrKqcXaBvWAhYR5SWIVCZ1wI_N3YvSd0VMuxAUqNdNAuIRGh9g3e42c3RkhtUMgUuPfDEk51wUcU3dbWsbO5ealPfJs667DlMDnYUOPkwJNnFeHv4o3NEjC2bGFIdI9O1I4a_jTUP7XzfCle2eVzA4XIIL2aoY2_m2eFsVOqIASDEaccHIKOLZID9Uv8K8j7VVie42fSCUGoIAlzDhmEG8Mis2-vihd3GVXqioUFX6f-XAStU2TsVsvk_eVy91EfKmh_eHA7bzzxliztG_QQgcAzi4d9wRPmWy7SB74wH8KKavbecMQ4HFCqyN4-st7dic3oA==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Investigating login issues**\\n\\nI’m trying to figure out why logging in is impossible. Maybe the user is already logged in, but only with a specific Chrome profile. I wonder if I could use that Chrome profile instead of Openclaw or extensions? But it seems like the profile isn't currently attached. Would using a Chrome profile that’s already logged in help? I need to look into the browser to check on existing tabs and see if an extension is required.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"卡点找到了：网页编辑这条路现在被飞书登录页拦住了，`openclaw` 管理浏览器里没你的登录态。  \n所以不是本王不动手，是现在这条浏览器实例进不去文档编辑态。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c1594e948196951d1f77dae229aa"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 还没插进去，卡点已经找到了：\n\n- 我想走网页编辑把图片按标题插回文档\n- 但当前浏览器实例打开文档时，进的是**飞书扫码登录页**\n- 也就是说，**现在这个浏览器没有你的飞书登录态**\n- 所以我暂时进不了文档编辑态，自然也没法精确插图\n\n现在最稳的解法有两个：\n\n### 方案 A：你把登录态给我\n最简单的是你在你自己的 Chrome 里把飞书文档打开并登录好，然后我接管那个已登录页面继续插图。\n\n如果你愿意，我就按这个走。\n\n### 方案 B：我先用工具链做“弱插入”\n也就是不用网页精确摆放，而是：\n- 先把图片按章节顺序插入文档\n- 不追求像网页拖拽那样绝对精确\n- 但内容顺序能对上\n\n---\n\n我建议你选 **A**，因为这样插出来最自然。\n\n你只要回我一句：\n- **走 A**\n\n本王就继续接你已登录的页面干。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c15968a881968d6be0664bce94fe"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1180,"output":401,"cacheRead":232448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":234029,"cost":{"input":0.002065,"output":0.005614,"cacheRead":0.040678399999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.048357399999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773322567533}}
