{"type":"message","id":"e69c7fff","parentId":"8f178618","timestamp":"2026-03-12T13:41:52.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering Chrome profiles**\n\nI’m thinking about how to manage different tabs in Chrome using profiles. It seems that utilizing status or tabs with these profiles could help with organization. I want to explore how profiles can separate work and personal activities effectively. This could involve looking into setting different bookmarks and settings for each profile to enhance the browsing experience! Let's see how that will improve productivity and keep things tidy!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c29cdbd08196ba4f51b934b65d60\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpssKfppomO4rVmo0gpvldUOXCs6xnGXtp9-OvtkKu6tGYZOlBw3_Htr2pw3SXFhZ9HfV-RlprVjtocJT6MIJ2z9siYYUh4Old2LfcSm5GTy8bUnGvV4jkGbYH6grmbC6K24alHyKsr-TzmmnzEkpGFy8oWO_FNE0xt_ME2FCpQWjU-2OYvNUslmVy56RdyE2CB8J6vDJ8Yr5IOTFWEEKBj7lVDk5JQu2dSUD3V5SyCJ-56-Wem47_E8fB09N8nIwae2P9nlrK994sOJhL-mi4kSL6S9Et4wvnaII3ei0gAJxtHO1o3famlizGw_NSKUFDQ_HSpoM_heyD8kfv9gSjetArsLUXWiuwyqYrJVjN8BGDIBmgrcic7wQ-KtsEV8GscFAgDorSWXCA4KV3h0azYC8_nl9Vdcvj9gdHqWPvGyd2L2U6IdTaJDphHzAGPuAL3kViqfi0nArOLWFaKacANjdIbUKZADzkWID1MwmK7HqNJmGkNYV9BNeV6vk3tQ3ycgLdoR02iTDQEPQ9M3ePCaUfr73zArtT9c_5V-7AuBcBJ0kZlDR6q3xj9Q2uPRCaArLvZXhqvqLKmAD1Uu4Y5VHrqD-CZ8rCmn3caXAiE34eWXqQqjL7UCruma3lbmsDvo9rqpgRDF2XT5xwfr3wM96HtXTJzUo_92g-LMUjCVeADjpNKOkBXjR6qveXaW23VNY3KGrOCQlayyS3b4O1DfikHOBhwnDKQXSmfyQjB41TyUSRis9v2jshGnV9MuMuN2CxlUGvcNI0P4F9Iy4FfcsSEpimHN5e6HmQEIaUvf0CzcVpyJy0bpTj2hSQzYB5A8HsB_gybRxf4xK9lDfEJsU22Dq0QTL7gmDXTIKd6DCONZ5ePj1mdOpCDDaaIYEWi2jc\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering Chrome profiles**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how to manage different tabs in Chrome using profiles. It seems that utilizing status or tabs with these profiles could help with organization. I want to explore how profiles can separate work and personal activities effectively. This could involve looking into setting different bookmarks and settings for each profile to enhance the browsing experience! Let's see how that will improve productivity and keep things tidy!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_MZvSNgOqGkootq0YFAQhkZ07|fc_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c29f536481969cd2b14fff3fcc2b","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"tabs","profile":"chrome","target":"host"},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"tabs\",\"profile\":\"chrome\",\"target\":\"host\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":222,"output":40,"cacheRead":233856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":234118,"cost":{"input":0.0003885,"output":0.00056,"cacheRead":0.0409248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.041873299999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773322901561}}
