em with unnecessary details. It feels right to keep the communication clear and straightforward. Let's see how that approach works out!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 行，这次我已经按你选的 **1** 执行完了：\n\n- **12 张图全部插进文档了**\n- 先保证文档里**有图、能看、能交付**\n- 不是精排版，但结果已经落地\n\n你现在刷新文档就能看到。  \n后面如果你哪天还想精修，本王再给你慢慢做“按章节精排”。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2c6a3c25081969113a519b145a8f3"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":5803,"output":131,"cacheRead":235392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":241326,"cost":{"input":0.01015525,"output":0.001834,"cacheRead":0.0411936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05318285}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773323931730}}
