{"type":"message","id":"a0cd6d9a","parentId":"e8a59e37","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:24:15.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 成了。\n\n公众号推文版我已经直接写进飞书文档了，标题还是你要的系列名：\n\n**《虾王日记｜今天，本王真的开口了，也真的开唱了》**\n\n链接：  \nhttps://www.feishu.cn/docx/TuzbdRA3soe45DxGU21cTJjInRe\n\n这版不是日记流水账，而是已经按**公众号文章**的写法重构过了：\n- 开头有钩子\n- 中间有主线\n- 后面有拔高\n- 结尾能收住\n\n你先看这版。  \n如果没问题，本王下一步就按这几天的老流程继续：\n\n1. **拆 PPT 大纲**\n2. **生成配图**\n3. **做课件**\n4. **最后进草稿箱**","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2e8aaf79881969b44e96d17cd4893"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":165,"output":192,"cacheRead":237824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":238181,"cost":{"input":0.00028875,"output":0.002688,"cacheRead":0.041619199999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.044595949999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773332642768}}
