{"type":"message","id":"98cd086c","parentId":"5bfbcea6","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:47:38.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 现在进度到这：\n\n- **公众号推文版**：已经写完并落到飞书文档了\n- **PPT 大纲**：也已经拆完了\n- **还没开始的部分**：配图生成和 PPT 合成\n\n所以本王不跟你装“快好了”——  \n现在属于：\n\n> **文案完成，课件骨架完成，视觉层还没开工。**\n\n也就是说，脑子和结构都定了，  \n差的是把它真正变成那套你能拿在手里的 PPT。\n\n如果你还继续推，本王下一步就是直接开图，不再聊天。","textSignature":"msg_05af7521743ea8dd0169b2ee255bbc81968ccca341fdb0f621"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":238375,"output":149,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":240060,"cost":{"input":0.41715625,"output":0.002086,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.41951105}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773334042423}}
